                </li>

                <li>
                    <a href="preference-search.jsp">내 취향 전시 찾기</a>
                </li>

                <li class="dropdown">
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="dropbtn">소식·참여</a>
                    <div class="dropdown-content">
